import React, { useEffect } from 'react'; import { Container, Form, Nav } from 'react-bootstrap'; let Header = () => { useEffect(() => { window.addEventListener("scroll", isscroll) }) let isscroll = () => { let header = document.querySelector(".header") if(window.scrollY >= 200) { header.classList.add("active") }else { header.classList.remove("active") } } return (
    home MOVIE TV SHOW WEB SERIES PRICING
) } export default Header
